WEBVTT

00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:32.309
I saw, over by the stove,

00:05:32.333 --> 00:05:37.768
this trunk that was just covered
in little pieces of driftwood.

00:05:37.792 --> 00:05:39.101
And I thought,

00:05:39.125 --> 00:05:41.143
"I'll try a question

00:05:41.167 --> 00:05:43.726
that he could answer without words."

00:05:43.750 --> 00:05:45.893
So I tried,

00:05:45.917 --> 00:05:47.518
"Jim,

00:05:47.542 --> 00:05:51.083
can you show me how water moves?"

00:05:52.833 --> 00:05:56.893
It was silent for a while,

00:05:56.917 --> 00:06:01.226
but then really slowly he took a step